  "update_count": 59,
  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nIf the AccessibilityTreeForViews flag is enabled, an |ax_tree_manager_| will be made based on the root_view[1]. And in ViewsAXTreeManager, a callback function will be post into SequencedTaskRunner[2], it will finally call[3] |GetUniqueId()| and access the root_view[4]. S"
}